<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.1. SLIPS 1-3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.1">言以詞[始LL]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.2">情以久。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.3">靡言不酬[讎LL]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.4">靡徳亡復。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.5">言 而苟，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.6">牆[墉CW]有耳。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.7">往言傷人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.8">來言傷己。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.9">言之善，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.10">足以終世。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.11">三世之福，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.12">不足以出芒。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-1a.13"></seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.2. SLIP 4"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-2a.1">口不慎</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-2a.2">而戶之 <不TZL> 閉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-2a.3">惡言報[復GDE]己</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-2a.4">而死無日。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.3. SLIPS 5-7"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.1">凡說之道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.2">急者為首。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.3">既得其急，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.4">言必有及之。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.5">及之而不可，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.6">必文以過[訛GDE]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.7">無令知我。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.8">破邦亡將，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-3a.9">流澤而行.</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.4. SLIPS 8-9"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-4a.1">竊钩者誅，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-4a.2">竊邦者為諸侯。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-4a.3">諸侯之門，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-4a.4">義士之所存.</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.5. SLIPS 10-11"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.1">車蓋之蔽[(酉 + 必+皿)LL] 翳[醢LL]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.2">不見江湖之水。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.3">匹婦遇[偶CW]夫，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.4">不知其鄉之小人君子。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.5">食韭</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-5a.6">惡知終其葉 [年CW] (世LL)。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.6. SLIPS 12-14"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.1">早與賢人，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.2">是謂浸行。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.3">賢人不在側，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.4">是謂迷惑。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.5">不與智謀，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.6">是謂自欺。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.7">早與智謀，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-6a.8">是謂重基。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.7. SLIPS 14-16"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.1">邦有巨雄，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.2">必先與之以為朋。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.3">雖難之而弗惡，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.4">必盡其故。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.5">盡之而疑，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.6">必(十+攴)[許TZL]裕裕其遷.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.7">如將有敗，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-7a.8">雄是為害[割GDE]。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.8. SLIPS 16-"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.1">利木陰者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.2">不折其枝。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.3">利其潴者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.4">不塞其溪。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.5">善使其下，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.6">若蚈蛩之足，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.7">眾而不害，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-8a.8">害[割GDE]而不仆。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.9. SLIPS 14-16"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.1">善事其上者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.2">若齒之事舌，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.3">而終弗衍[譴CW]。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.4">善[事其下]者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.5">若兩輪之相轉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.6">而終不相敗。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.7">善使其民者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.8">若四時，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.9">一遣一來，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-9a.10">而民弗害也。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.10. SLIPS 14-16"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.1">山亡嶞</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.2">則阤，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.3">城無蓑</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.4">則阤，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.5">士無友</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.6">不可。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.7">君有謀臣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.8">則壤地不削。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.9">士有謀友，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-10a.10">則言談不弱。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN, YUCONG 4, 18.11. SLIPS 14-16"><pb xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.1">雖勇力聞於邦，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.2">不如材，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.3">金玉盈室</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.4">不如謀，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.5">眾強甚多</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.6">不如時。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0031_tls_001-11a.7">故謀為可貴。</seg></p>

